.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-FEE-EARNED-VARIANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-fee-earned-variance \- FEAT-2951 channel-fee-earned-variance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-fee-earned-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the variance of fees earned across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2951).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fBfee_earned_variance_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
